Data Source

The expression profiles of mRNAs in the colon of HFD-induced C57BL/6J mice were deposited into the Gene Expression Omnibus (GEO) database under accession number GSE249390.

Generating Figure 4

The downloaded GSE249390 dataset was uploaded to the BGI Biosys online platform for analysis. This analysis generated Figure 4, visualizing mRNA expression profiles and their biological relevance.
